name: com.castsoftware.uc.aip2hl
title: CAST AIP to Highlight Tool
description: CAST AIP to Highlight is used to analyze, in Highlight, source code that has previously been analyzed using AIP. To work properly the application must have at least one snapshot in the Application Analytics Dashboard (AAD). This package includes a Jenkins plugin, allowing the automatic rescan of applications into Hightlight.
